---
// Newsletter subscription CTA block - inserted at bottom of every article
---

<section class="subscribe-cta no-print">
	<div class="subscribe-cta-inner">
		<h3>訂閱 Nephro Decisions</h3>
		<p>每月 25 日一封。新文、查核修訂、台灣健保實務。3 分鐘讀完。</p>
		<form
			action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/nephrodecisions"
			method="post"
			target="popupwindow"
			class="subscribe-cta-form"
		>
			<label for="subscribe-cta-email" class="sr-only">電子郵件地址</label>
			<input type="email" name="email" id="subscribe-cta-email" placeholder="your@email.com" required aria-label="電子郵件地址" />
			<button type="submit">訂閱</button>
		</form>
		<p class="subscribe-cta-note">也可透過 <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a> 追蹤</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.subscribe-cta {
		margin: 2.5em 0 1em;
		padding: 1.8em 1.5em;
		background: #f0f4f3;
		border-radius: 10px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
	}
	.subscribe-cta-inner {
		max-width: 500px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.subscribe-cta h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.3em;
		font-size: 1.15em;
		color: var(--accent-dark);
	}
	.subscribe-cta > .subscribe-cta-inner > p {
		margin: 0 0 1em;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
	}
	.subscribe-cta-form {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.4em;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.subscribe-cta-form input[type="email"] {
		flex: 1;
		min-width: 180px;
		max-width: 280px;
		padding: 0.5em 0.9em;
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}
	.subscribe-cta-form button {
		padding: 0.5em 1.2em;
		background: var(--accent);
		color: #fff;
		border: none;
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		font-weight: 600;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	.subscribe-cta-form button:hover {
		background: var(--accent-dark);
	}
	.subscribe-cta-note {
		margin: 0.6em 0 0 !important;
		font-size: 0.78em !important;
	}
	.subscribe-cta-note a {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	@media print {
		.no-print {
			display: none !important;
		}
	}
</style>
